ng visible results in just 3 minutes. FDA-cleared, portable, and perfect for all skin types.\"<\/p>","rte_content":"","city_text":"","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/SPA_BEAUTY_today_logo.png","logo_height":40,"class":""}},"text_9zQXL3":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p><em>“MagicMoon in the Top 10 Best Red Light Therapy Devices We Tested, Approved by Dermatologists” <\/em><\/p>","rte_content":"","city_text":"","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/GLAMOUR_1.png","logo_height":32,"class":""}}},"block_order":["text_BmJgbC","text_8iR3UQ","text_PhxdcE","text_J63G8b","text_hfeQYD","text_nW7cXH","text_ejnxLR","text_9zQXL3"],"name":"Feature Section","settings":{"background":"#fafafa","text_color":"#000000","tite":"Trusted by"}},"product_counter_section_texNL6":{"type":"product-counter-section","settings":{"padding_top":false,"padding_bottom":true,"background":"#202020","title":"APPROVED BY REAL PEOPLE","sub_text":""}},"product-recommendations":{"type":"product-recommendations","disabled":true,"settings":{"heading":"<p>You May Also Like<\/p>","link":"Explore","button_link":"","products_limit":3,"border_top":true,"image_ratio":"landscape","image_fit":"contain","show_secondary_image":true,"show_vendor":true,"show_desc":true,"show_sku":false,"columns_mobile":"1"}},"technical_specification_section_QFCtep":{"type":"technical-specification-section","settings":{}},"new_video_section_xa3GqH":{"type":"new-video-section","settings":{"paddingtop":false,"padBottom":true,"title":"","background":"","video_url":""}},"cosmoprof_awards_section_WcKzBg":{"type":"cosmoprof-awards-section","blocks":{"block_LJ447n":{"type":"block","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/CosmoTrends_2024.png"}},"block_8TUDHt":{"type":"block","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/CPNA24_CosmoprofAwards_Winner_web_240604_v0-03_3.png"}},"block_nRfdVy":{"type":"block","settings":{}},"block_cHRJKf":{"type":"block","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/CosmoTrends_2025.png"}},"block_PCFpRe":{"type":"block","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/CosmoTrends_Miami_2025.png"}},"block_CdEaG9":{"type":"block","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Cosmo_trends_a9e5520f-9d41-493c-989b-a3655c2f071c.png"}}},"block_order":["block_LJ447n","block_8TUDHt","block_nRfdVy","block_cHRJKf","block_PCFpRe","block_CdEaG9"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"title":"AWARDS"}},"171800536627f40222":{"type":"apps","blocks":{"okendo_reviews_carousel_YRf9qC":{"type":"shopify:\/\/apps\/okendo\/blocks\/reviews-carousel\/bb689e69-ea70-4661-8fb7-ad24a2e23c29","settings":{"show_heading":true,"heading":"","badge_link":"","product":"{{product}}"}}},"block_order":["okendo_reviews_carousel_YRf9qC"],"custom_css":[".spaced-section {padding-top: 50px !important; padding-bottom: 0px;}"],"settings":{"include_margins":true}},"service_icon_hEBpVU":{"type":"service-icon","blocks":{"item_Kga3Jy":{"type":"item","settings":{"custom_icon":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Frame_2087326400.svg","title":"Clinically<br>proven results"}},"item_zy8rkD":{"type":"item","settings":{"custom_icon":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Layer_2.svg","title":"ONE YEAR<br>WARRANTY"}},"item_3MQRnk":{"type":"item","settings":{"custom_icon":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Layer_2_1.svg","title":"Dermatologist<br>recommended"}},"item_q7wJpc":{"type":"item","settings":{"custom_icon":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Layer_1.svg","title":"FDA<br>Cleared"}},"item_q4XbdK":{"type":"item","settings":{"custom_icon":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Asset_1.svg","title":"Self-Timed<br>Treatment"}}},"block_order":["item_Kga3Jy","item_zy8rkD","item_3MQRnk","item_q7wJpc","item_q4XbdK"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"bgcolor":"#ffffff","textcolor":"#828282","paddTop":true,"padBottom":true,"customClass":"","title":"SKINCARE ROOTED IN INNOVATION, <br>PROVEN BY SCIENCE"}},"product_service_icon_MJNa3n":{"type":"product-service-icon","disabled":true,"name":"Product Service Icon","settings":{"bgcolor":"#ffffff","textcolor":"#828282","paddTop":false,"padBottom":true,"customClass":"","title":"SKINCARE ROOTED IN INNOVATION, <br>PROVEN BY SCIENCE"}},"testimonials_section_LGVAAk":{"type":"testimonials-section","blocks":{"text_kTHQmJ":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p><em>Just did my treatment and emptied one of the serums. I wanted to cry a little so I’m thrilled to get more. I can feel the tightening as I write this.<\/em><\/p>","rte_content":"","city_text":"Christian - Los Angeles, CA","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Layer_1.png"}},"text_QTV8qq":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p><em>I’ve been using Metamorphosis exosome serums for a few months now, and the results have been amazing! I’ve essentially stopped getting Botox—thanks to the serum, my fine lines have noticeably decreased. My absolute favorite part? My lips look so hydrated and lush!<\/em><\/p>","rte_content":"","city_text":"Susan - Hilton Head Island, SC","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Layer_1.png"}},"text_EqaVYa":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p><em>This is more than just skincare—it’s science-backed skin regeneration. The use of exosomes and stem cells takes this product into an entirely different category. You’re not just masking signs of aging; you’re giving your skin the tools to repair itself on a cellular level. <\/em><\/p><p><em>If you’re serious about transformative skincare, this serum is a must.<\/em><\/p>","rte_content":"","city_text":"Kathy - Charleston, SC","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Layer_1.png"}},"text_XWRtLU":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p><em>As a 60-year-old woman who has been dedicated to a robust skincare and red light therapy regimen for many years, I can honestly say that applying SkinEXCELLENCE serum before my RLT sessions has been a game-changer. My skin now feels regenerated with improved hydration, enhanced elasticity and a more even toned glow. This powerhouse serum is my new best!!<\/em><\/p>","rte_content":"","city_text":"Tracey - Tampa, FL","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Layer_1.png"}},"text_EntmXA":{"type":"text","disabled":true,"settings":{"text":"<p><em>“The LushLips hydrogel mask is a game changer for my lips! It provides immediate hydration, leaving my lips feeling incredibly soft and smooth. I always use these when my lips are feeling dry or after being in the sun for a while!....<\/em><\/p>","rte_content":"<p><em>“The LushLips hydrogel mask is a game changer for my lips! It provides immediate hydration, leaving my lips feeling incredibly soft and smooth. I always use these when my lips are feeling dry or after being in the sun for a while! The lip masks fit perfectly without slipping, unlike other lip masks I’ve tried that fall down my face. After just one use, my lips feel rejuvenated.”<\/em><\/p><p><em>Also, “SuperStar red light pimple patches are absolutely amazing! And this is unlike any other pimple patches, because you don’t have to leave it on for hours to see results! It significantly reduces the size and redness of my pimples right after use! It is so easy to use and the effective results have made it an everyday staple in my skincare routine.  I can’t believe how quickly it can clear up my skin! Also, it came in the cutest packaging and is so easy to bring with you anywhere you go! Definitely my new go-to pimple patch!”<\/em><\/p>","city_text":"Tory, Washington, DC","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Layer_1.png"}},"text_x6PcEt":{"type":"text","disabled":true,"settings":{"text":"<p><em>“The search for the perfect eye treatment is now over! Metamorphosis MagicMoon Eye Evolution is a game changer! Actually, it is a life changer! Nothing has come close to the remarkable results I’ve experienced in a short amount.....<\/em><\/p>","rte_content":"<p><em>“The search for the perfect eye treatment is now over! Metamorphosis MagicMoon Eye Evolution is a game changer! Actually, it is a life changer! Nothing has come close to the remarkable results I’ve experienced in a short amount of time (a couple of weeks) and requires no needles, no downtime and can be done at any time of the day.  They are engineered with convenience in mind: rechargeable, easy to clean, small enough to fit into a makeup bag or handbag. I couldn’t be more thrilled with the results. I can stop wasting time and money with eye treatments, creams or procedures.  MagicMoon gives me the youthful, refreshed appearance I’ve always wanted in just 3 minutes per day!”<\/em><\/p><p><em>Also:  “Aging can do cruel things to a woman’s body.  Slight changes happen over time. One day, you look in the mirror and hardly recognize the face staring back at you.  This was the case with my lips.  Small lines and thinning set in, and being needle adverse, I thought I would just have to live with it.  LushLips has saved the day though!  Having personally experienced Magic Moons, I am sold on the company, so investing in LushLips was a no-brainer.  After 2 weeks, I can tell a difference! Small lines are disappearing, the corners of my mouth are softening and this is without any needles or downtime!  LushLips takes 3 minutes, is painless and revives my lips!”<\/em><\/p>","city_text":"Diane, Atlanta","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Layer_1.png"}}},"block_order":["text_kTHQmJ","text_QTV8qq","text_EqaVYa","text_XWRtLU","text_EntmXA","text_x6PcEt"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"background-img":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/image_161.png","text_color":"#ffffff","tite":"TESTIMONIALS"}},"pioneering_synergy_skincare_pqeLc7":{"type":"pioneering-synergy-skincare","disabled":true,"name":"Pioneering Section","settings":{"img":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Ultimate_glow_kit_1920x1080_1.png","mobile_img":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Group_1321dgfdg314892_1.png","text":"Pioneering <br>Synergy skincare","sub_text":"Unparalleled skin rejuvenation","content":"<p>The world’s first duo to combine targeted Red Light and Sonic Vibration  technology with Exosomes, this innovation delivers unmatched skin rejuvenation. By stimulating cellular activity and enhancing Exosome uptake, this luxurious pairing ensures more precise and effective delivery of potent molecules for visibly firmer, brighter skin.<\/p>","btn_text":"VIEW MORE DETAILS","btn_url":"shopify:\/\/products\/ultimate-glow-kit"}},"product_plumper_slider_y7JR7J":{"type":"product-plumper-slider","settings":{}},"product_faq_section_x7EGqy":{"type":"product-faq-section","settings":{"show_line_separator":true,"show_image":false,"content":"<p>Everything you need to know about our skincare and light therapy innovations<\/p>","button_text":"VIEW ALL FAQ","button_link":"shopify:\/\/pages\/faqs"}},"shop_by_category_4ayVq8":{"type":"shop-by-category","blocks":{"image_picker_VHrH4g":{"type":"image_picker","settings":{"img_link":"shopify:\/\/collections\/led-light-devices","image_category":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Metamorphosis_-_PDP_Silicone_Patches.png","title_caption":"LED DEVICES","text_color":"#696969"}},"image_picker_t7AN6j":{"type":"image_picker","settings":{"img_link":"shopify:\/\/collections\/hydrogel-masks","image_category":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Metamorphosis_-_PDP_Silicone_Patches_-_Update_3_images_for__Shop_by_category.png","title_caption":"HYDROGEL MASKS","text_color":"#696969"}},"image_picker_Fr8dDG":{"type":"image_picker","settings":{"img_link":"shopify:\/\/collections\/sculpt-lift","image_category":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Metamorphosis-red-gift-bag-butterfly-gifting-packaging.png","title_caption":"SCULPT AND LIFT KIT","text_color":"#696969"}}},"block_order":["image_picker_VHrH4g","image_picker_t7AN6j","image_picker_Fr8dDG"],"settings":{"padding_top":true,"padding_bottom":true,"back_color":"#ffffff","heading_color":"#000000","text_color":"#000000","shop_title":"SHOP BY CATEGORY","sub_text":"Discover the art of transformation with our cutting-edge collection.  From the rejuvenating power of LEDs to deeply nourishing and targeted hydrogel masks and the sculpting precision of our lift kit, each creation is designed to work in perfect harmony.","btn_text":"SHOP ALL DEVICEs","btn_url":""}},"service_icon_ipqeXx":{"t